title: Falcons soar back into playoff hunt, run over Ridgeview
text:
Falcons soar back into playoff hunt, run over Ridgeview 
Sat, Oct 24, 2015 @ 12:21 am 
The Times-Union 
MENENDEZ 28 
RIDGEVIEW 14 
Ryan Riceâ€™s two touchdowns sparked a balanced rushing attack as Menendez returned to the playoff hunt by defeating visiting Ridgeview (1-7, 0-4 District 5-5A). ... Jevon Floyd rushed for 101 yards and a touchdown, quarterback Darian Oxendine gained 105 more and Tyler Roden also scored for the Falcons (4-4, 2-2), who rushed for 327 yards as a team. ... Matthew Denegal set up a Menendez touchdown with a second-quarter interception. ... River Walker threw two touchdown passes for the Panthers.
